org.jscsi.target.settings

Class KeySet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jscsi.target.settings.KeySet

  • public final class KeySet
extends Object
    KeySet objects are used by Entry instances for storing all keys that might be used to negotiate the parameter managed by the Entry. Individual keys are represented as String objects.

    Although most parameters are associated with just one key, there are some exceptions, hence justifying the added complexity of using a dedicated class for managing keys in favor of simply using multiple String objects.

    Author:
    Andreas Ergenzinger
